Package: hcruR
Title: Estimate, Compare, and Visualize the Healthcare Resource Utilization for Real World Evidence
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Maheshkumar", "Umbarkar", email = "maheshubr30@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to estimate and compare healthcare resource utilization by domain and cohort. Supports cohort-based event counting, cost summary, time window analysis, and plotting for Real World Evidence studies.
